	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You hum as you magically draw a small amount of wax from tiny colored candles into the air. They burn rapidly, then form glowing balls of light that you can move and combine.</em></p><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong> </p><p>You create one of the following effects with glowing light. Whichever form you choose, each light sheds &amp;reference[dimlight] in a 10-foot radius. The spell ends if you cast this spell again.</p><ul><li><p>You create up to four torch-sized lights within range, making them appear as torches, lanterns, or glowing orbs that hover in the air for the duration.</p></li><li><p>You combine the four lights into one glowing vaguely humanoid or beast-like form of Medium size or smaller.</p></li><li><p>You create glowing letters in a 20 ft. cube. The letters are large, and can only spell out a few short words or about 15 letters.</p><p></p></li></ul><p>As a bonus action on your turn, you can move the lights up to 60 feet to a new spot within range. If you have more than one light, each light must be within 20 feet of another light created by this spell, and a light winks out if it exceeds the spell's range.</p>",
			"chat": ""
		},
